Begin RFC:
RFC: 0.0.0
Title: Security Policy
Author: Richeve Bebedor <richeve.bebedor+vs-scripts@gmail.com>
Status: Draft
Created: 2025-12-20

1. Reporting Vulnerabilities:

   If you discover a security vulnerability within this project, please send an
   email to Richeve Bebedor at richeve.bebedor+vs-scripts@gmail.com.

2. Policy:

   All security vulnerabilities will be promptly addressed. We maintain a proactive
   stance on the security of the install-node-version script and related assets.
End RFC:
